train module¶

train.train_with_YOLO(hp: dict)¶

Train YOLO using the Stanford car dataset and save it to an S3 bucket.

Parameters:

hp (dict) – A dictionary of hyperparameters.

Returns:

True if training was successful and the model was saved in the S3 bucket, False otherwise.

Return type:

bool
